    <title>Feature #183 (New): Include the ability to embed references to other OSHW projects in BoM module</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="http://opendesignengine.net/issues/183"/>
    <id>http://opendesignengine.net/issues/183</id>
    <updated>2013-09-18T16:05:05+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>J. Simmons</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">
&lt;p&gt;As OSHW projects grow in scale and complexity, some projects will become components of other projects (Thingiverse objects come to mind as an example).  Bill of Materials components should be able to easily point at OSHW projects as components and take advantage of metadata from the source sites.&lt;/p&gt;    </content>
